Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(1110,398)\c&HF2F2F2&\3c&H8B2A27&\fad(0,200)}"Ozu initiation"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, the sea level continued to rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,submerging most places worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately with Kyoto being a basin, it still stands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if the water level continues to rise, eventually the waters will exceed the mountains and surge in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sinking this Rakuyou after five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The conference at Kyoto prefecture continued day and night,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,concluding that I, Captain Higuchi and my crew, am entrusted with our fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will depart to discover the reason of the founder to save Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the engineer, and additionally, the harpooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the head interpreter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you speak with feeling, communication with anyone is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the discovering to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all the ladies, I'll be leaving Japan shortly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll definitely be back, and so, "See you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fire the wave motion gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the South Pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be that the ice melted causing the sea level to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it really melt so rapidly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more concerned for our health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't like raw vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, please do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beer after work, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have shark fin and caviar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an island of ice, of course it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The South Pole should continue even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must always be catching colds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd make it big selling machines that make icebergs but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they would sell better during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I'll get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, go pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Master? Er- Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born entirely for our encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-san, she's not whom you seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er- Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bit of business to attend to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you to take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the elephants will drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll guide them to the Okazaki Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May fate allow us to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a role in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cooked this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able able to eat shark fin, caviar, and foie gras at a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is delicious, this Iberian pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}However, from here on we're nearing the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's melting the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In literature, it was "red bean initiation," written "small bean initiation."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he's mistaken it for "Ozu initiation."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born in the Kansai region, so he might be waiting for a tsukkomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate we'll be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is normally a land submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, what is it that you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsatisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remain unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you actually want to eat red beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you want a meal but munch on snacks, your stomach feels unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the stomach full, being able to eat a dessert is not a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, but give me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's canned red beans, enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Sorry. You let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rainbow, how romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Kyoto be saved with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this truly the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all of Earth's ice melted, it may become too hot for man and we might perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start, a floating continent may not have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Riding the waves smoothly, going with the current is for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That story is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the story's structure to the scenario up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}I mean, in my opinion, this dream's logic is...
